Feature: addition using Scenario Outline

Scenario Outline: Add two numbers
    * def result = <num1> + <num2>
    * match result == <sum>
    * print 'Addition:', <num1>, '+', <num2>, '=', result

Examples:
    | num1 | num2 | sum |
    | 2    | 3    | 5   |
    | 10   | 5    | 15  |
    | 7    | 8    | 15  |.


























































































































































































































